technology association of georgia  honorary chairman financial services roundtable scholarship foundation designated first presidential fellow columbus state university  charter recipient georgia ethics in business award  the award is now known as the blanchard award in business ethics southeastern university doctorate of humane letters  the eddie sams award university of georgia golf team  rozier dedwylder leadership award uptown columbus inc  lifetime achievement award technology association of georgia  woodruff award columbus chamber of commerce  vanlandingham award georgia council on economic education  martin luther king jr unity award delta lambda chapter of alpha phi alpha fraternity inc educational foundation  “most influential georgians hall of fame” georgia trend magazine  “ most influential people in financial services” us banker magazine  beta gamma sigma international honoree award  “georgian of the year” georgia trend magazine  “most respected ceo” in the state georgia trend magazine  summary jim served as chairman and ceo of synovus a multibillion dollar financial services company based in columbus georgia  synovus bank divisions provide commercial and retail banking investment and mortgage services to customers in georgia alabama south carolina florida and tennessee  in  he formed a partnership with columbus state university’s cunningham center for leadership development to create the jim blanchard leadership forum the mission of the forum is to provide columbus and the region the opportunity to interact with some of the most influential political military and business leaders in the world to create a synergy that raises both the local and national standard for leadership development previous speakers at the forum include president george w bush former first lady laura bush former secretary of state condoleezza rice former secretary of defense robert gates former us senators sam nunn and zell miller former speaker of the house newt gingrich author ken blanchard author john maxwell former secretary of state colin powell general david petraeus and former us attorney general griffin bell “one of the greatest gifts i can offer to our country is an investment in leadership  we want to provide a forum where leaders can be exposed to the best and brightest minds in the world today” said blanchard blanchard currently serves as chairman board of advisors jordanblanchard capital llc a firm that focuses on investing in small businesses in the manufacturing distribution and business services sectors visit the tag fintech society page tag titanium sponsors tag platinum sponsors tag gold sponsors  recipient  jimmy blanchard update profile contact about board of directors menu home chapters  societies events training resources tech careers news  press membership view all events month at a glance  major events sponsorship opportunities tag sales leadership awards data science  analytics innovation awards career fairs executive online auction  tag celebrates gas inc  fastest growing private companies cio roundtable series clevel programs tag cybersecurity simulation bytes for bites tag day of service tag crm  cx the customer experience journey seventh annual tag diversity leadership awards excalibur awards tag fintech ga health it leadership summit georgia technology summit top  tag north fulton tag north metro tag perimeter tag ssa impact awards stem education awards tagit golf tournament techie kk runwalk venture atlanta tag young pros one in a millennial awards tag iot symposium  geek out marketing technology women in business north america summit titanium sponsors research  insights stay connected with hub resource links georgia it job trends state of the industry report technology industry maps regional technology maps government affairs affiliate partners tecna save with ups shipping service providers membership directory attention employers job seekers tech jobs  powered by techfetch technology industry jobs career fairs